(164, 274, 'Shear Marks 長不高的孩子', 'vimeo-id-163396263', '			<p class="intro-text">\r\n			The lines marked on the lamppost, which records the height of Chi, carry his childhood memories in\r\n			</p>\r\n			', '\r\n			<div class="vimeo-item content">\r\n			<div class="player"><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/163396263?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0&color=90d5ec" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe></div><p>The lines marked on the lamppost, which records the height of Chi, carry his childhood memories in the era of resettlement. The frivolousness of youth, the incipient love, the past with little regrets, reappear in his mind’s eye like a flash of light, lighting up the passionate childlike innocence of his heart once again.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n刻在燈柱上的身高線，盛載著主角阿志於徙置時代的兒<br />\r\n時往事。年少輕狂，剛萌芽的愛情，略帶遺憾的住事，霎眼如火花般掠過眼前，再次燃點起那顆埋藏在心底灼熱的童心。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n---<br />\r\nACHIEVEMENTS<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// THE 21ST IFVA AWARDS (ANIMATION CATEGORY) [2016 | Hong Kong] //<br />\r\n– Sliver Award<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// 17TH DIGICON6 ASIA [2016 | Japan] //<br />\r\n– HONG KONG Silver<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// CARTOONS ON THE BAY [2016 | Italy] //<br />\r\n– Selected<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// HONG KONG ICT AWARDS 2016 [2016 | Hong Kong] //<br />\r\n– Special Mention (Directing)<br />\r\n– Special Mention (Story / Screenplay)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n---<br />\r\nCREDIT<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// ANIMATION 動畫 //<br />\r\nKwok Man Ho 郭文浩<br />\r\nLam Ho Tak 林昊德<br />\r\nNg Kai Chung 吳啓忠<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// DUBBING 配音 //<br />\r\nChi 阿志 – Shum Hau Yi 岑巧怡<br />\r\nLing 小玲 – Chou On Tung 周安彤<br />\r\nTeeth Boy 哨牙強 – Shum Hau Yi 岑巧怡<br />\r\nMother 媽媽 – Lau Yuk Ling 劉玉玲<br />\r\nPolice 警察 – Ng Kai Chung 吳啓忠<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// SCRIPT 劇本 //<br />\r\nChou On Tung 周安彤<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// STORY 故事 //<br />\r\nPaperbox Creations<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// ORIGINAL MUSIC COMPOSER 原創音樂 //<br />\r\nKelvin Lau 水牛<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// SOUND DIRECTOR & MIXER 錄音及混音 //<br />\r\nLi Chi Fung 李志峰<br />\r\nLee Hoi Wah 李海華<br />\r\n<br />\r\n// SPECIAL THANKS 特別鳴謝 //<br />\r\nHKDEA 香港數碼娛樂協會<br />\r\nCreate HK 創意香港<br />\r\nHKPC 生產力促進局<br />\r\nTF:vs:JS 談風再說<br />\r\nGee Luen 8B 志聯 8B<br />\r\n<br />\r\n---<br />\r\n2015 Paperbox Creations Limited<br />\r\nwww.paperboxcreations.com<br />\r\nwww.facebook.com/paperboxcreations</p>\r\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 42, 'Paperbox Creations', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 42, 42, '2016-05-05 09:02:31', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"left","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"http:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/163396263","urlatext":"(Source Vimeo)","targeta":"1","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 2, 42, '', '', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
