(231, 404, 'by the desert sand', 'vimeo-id-165194945', '			<p class="intro-text">\r\n			Voici le film "by the desert sand" , un film alliant exploration, surf et kitesurf à travers\r\n			</p>\r\n			', '\r\n			<div class="vimeo-item content">\r\n			<div class="player"><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/165194945?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0&color=90d5ec" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe></div><p>Voici le film "by the desert sand" , un film alliant exploration, surf et kitesurf à travers l\'ouest du sahara. En parcourant plus de 4000 kms de pistes à la recherche des meilleures conditions mais surtout des plus perdus, nous avons profiter de moments et de paysages hors du commun.<br />\r\nretrouvez des photos et videos sur https://www.facebook.com/Freeride-Aventure-1610804012512920/?ref=ts&fref=ts<br />\r\net bon voyage !!!<br />\r\nBy the desert sand is an exploration across western sahara to discover best and lost surf and kitespots. With more than 4000 kms offroad, we enjoyed amazing moments and incredible landscapes.<br />\r\nYou can follow the story with pictures and videos on: https://www.facebook.com/Freeride-Aventure-1610804012512920/?ref=ts&fref=ts<br />\r\nsee you later and good trip !<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThanks to www.liquidforcekites.com<br />\r\n                   www.transporter-garage.com</p>\r\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 42, 'alex campet', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"left","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"http:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/165194945","urlatext":"(Source Vimeo)","targeta":"1","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_posi