(246, 422, 'Don\'t Walk', 'vimeo-id-165457784', '\n			<p class="intro-text">\n			A girl has to cut her night short, she resorts to red wine and poster ripping. Music by Indigo Sky\n			</p>\n			', '\n			<div class="vimeo-item content">\n			<div class="player"><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/165457784?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0&color=90d5ec" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe></div><p>A girl has to cut her night short, she resorts to red wine and poster ripping.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMusic by Indigo Sky<br />\r\niTunes - https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/dont-walk-single/id1110447669www.indigoskyofficial.com<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDirected, filmed and edited by Tolli Myers<br />\r\nStarring Tabitha Jones and Sean Davies<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEquipment<br />\r\n--------------<br />\r\nSony A7s<br />\r\nCanon Glass<br />\r\nGlidecam HD4000</p>\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 42, 'Tolli Myers', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '{"targeta":"1","urla":"http:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/165457784","urlatext":"(Source Vimeo)","targetb":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetc":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":""}', '{}', 1, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{"tags":null}', 0, '*', ''),
(247, 423, 'Ivan Raña - Libre', 'vimeo-id-165475952', '\n			<p class="intro-text">\n			On my own way es un proyecto audiovisual sobre Ivan Raña, sus vivencias, entrenos, costumbres,\n			</p>\n			', '\n			<div class="vimeo-item content">\n			<div class="player"><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/165475952?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0&color=90d5ec" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe></div><p>On my own way es un proyecto audiovisual sobre Ivan Raña, sus vivencias, entrenos, costumbres, refleja el día a día del triatleta profesional desde una visión íntima y cercana. Consta de diferentes capítulos que irán rodando a lo largo del año en las diferentes paradas competitivas, Lanzarote, Brasil, Madrid, entre otras para terminar el año en el Ironman de Kona (Hawaii).<br />\r\nEl primer capítulo "LIBRE", es una presentación personal y profesional de Ivan, rodado en la isla de Lanzarote, nos muestra el día a día de sus entrenos, se interna en los pensamientos más personales del deportista y nos cuenta sus aspiraciones y próximas metas. On my own way es un proyecto de @ginesdiaz y @adrianrodd.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n“On My Own Way” is the name of the audiovisual project about Ivan Rana.   This interesting and informative video project shares his everyday experiences,  feelings and reactions.  It charts his training sessions and routines.  This video lets you into the daily life of the professional triathlete and what keeps them going day in day out.<br />\r\n The video is made up of different times and events and races throughout the whole season.  Races and training from places like Lanzarote, Brasil, Madrid and many other places finishing with  the Ironman World Championship in Kona (Hawaii, USA).<br />\r\n The first video of the series of videos is called “Free”.  The video shows his day to day training and and goes into his deepest thoughts.  He tells us all about his upcoming goals.<br />\r\n <br />\r\n“On My Own Way” is a Project filmed and produced by Gines Diaz and Adrian Rodd.</p>\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 42, 'Adrian Rodd', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '{"targeta":"1","urla":"http:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/165475952","urlatext":"(Source Vimeo)","targetb":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetc":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":""}', '{}', 1, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{"tags":null}', 0, '*', ''),
