(295, 473, 'Google Analytics Dashboards for Joomla with JA Google Analytics Module', 'rss-id-google-analytics-dashboards-for-joomla-with-ja-google-analytics-module', '\n			<p class="intro-text">\n			Since we developed Joomla Admin template - JA Admin, we have been recieving requests to develop\n			</p>\n			', '\n			<div class="rss-item content">\n			<p>Since we developed Joomla Admin template - <a href="https://www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-admin" title="Joomla admin template">JA Admin</a>, we have been recieving requests to develop tools to make Joomla backend more practical and information rich. Almost everyone uses Google Analytics for their sites and usually needs to login to Google Analytics separately to see how the site is doing in general.</p> <p>The google analytics module that we previewed with JA Admin was a very basic one and so we have worked upon it to make it provide specific information related to routine analytics. Thus came the idea to develop specific dashboards for specific analytics view.</p><img class="rss-img ja-social-img" src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joomlart/blog/~4/GUu-MpPkuzg" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 42, '', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"float_fulltext":"","float_intro":"","image_intro":"images\\/jasocial_feed\\/01c159d20298190d64eb9abffa48f457.jpg","image_intro_alt":"Google Analytics Dashboards for Joomla with JA","image_intro_caption":"Google Analytics Dashboards for Joomla with JA","image_fulltext":"images\\/jasocial_feed\\/01c159d20298190d64eb9abffa48f457.jpg","image_fulltext_alt":"Google Analytics Dashboards for Joomla with JA","image_fulltext_caption":"Google Analytics Dashboards for Joomla with JA"}', '{"targeta":"1","urla":"http:\\/\\/feedproxy.google.com\\/~r\\/joomlart\\/blog\\/~3\\/GUu-MpPkuzg\\/google-analytics-dashboards-for-joomla-with-ja-google-analytics-module","urlatext":"(Source rss)","tar