(296, 474, '18 Joomla templates package updated & JA K2 Filter v 1.2.3 released', 'rss-id-18-joomla-templates-package-updated-ja-k2-filter-v-1-2-3-released', '\n			<p class="intro-text">\n			Hi guys, Joomla 3.6.2 has been released to fix some issues relate to sessions on PHP 5.3 and email\n			</p>\n			', '\n			<div class="rss-item content">\n			<p>Hi guys,</p> <p>Joomla 3.6.2 has been released to fix some issues relate to sessions on PHP 5.3 and email cloaking bugs. We tested and exported quickstart packages for framework and 17 Joomla templates, these templates have been tested for Joomla 3.6.2 and no bugs were found, so the version remains unchanged and only the quickstart package has been updated to include Joomla 3.6.2. We will test and export more templates in coming days. In addition, we also released <strong>JA K2 Filter component version 1.2.3</strong> with new feature, some improvement and bug fixes.</p><img class="rss-img ja-social-img" src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joomlart/blog/~4/rwVjaCmib-o" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 42, '', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"float_fulltext":"","float_intro":"","image_intro":"images\\/jasocial_feed\\/ceb5a354151ccfb6361933c682845e16.jpg","image_intro_alt":"18 Joomla templates package updated & JA K2 Filter","image_intro_caption":"18 Joomla templates package updated & JA K2 Filter","image_fulltext":"images\\/jasocial_feed\\/ceb5a354151ccfb6361933c682845e16.jpg","image_fulltext_alt":"18 Joomla templates package updated & JA K2 Filter","image_fulltext_caption":"18 Joomla templates package updated & JA K2 Filter"}', '{"targeta":"1","urla":"http:\\/\\/feedproxy.google.com\\/~r\\/joomlart\\/blog\\/~3\\/rwVjaCmib-o\\/18-joomla-templates-package-updated-ja-k2-filter-v-1-2-3-released","urlatext":"(Source rss)","targetb":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetc":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":""}', '{}', 1, 0, '', '', 1