(307, 485, 'Thanks - JA Joomla Site Builder Alpha 2000+ downloads in 2 days. New version released today', 'rss-thanks-ja-joomla-site-builder-alpha-2000-downloads-in-2-days-new-version-released-today', '\n			<p class="intro-text">\n			Hi guys, We are so happy that our JA Joomla Site Builder Alpha release got lots of good feedback\n			</p>\n			', '\n			<div class="rss-item content">\n			<p>Hi guys,</p> <p>We are so happy that our <a href="https://www.joomlart.com/ja-builder" title="joomla site builder">JA Joomla Site Builder</a> Alpha release got lots of good feedback from you guys, over 2000 downloads so far. Today we released version Alpha 2 with bug fixes and improvements.</p> <ul class="ja-checklist"> <li>Add meta to header to fix responsive issue on iOS and Android</li> <li>Add router to fix the publish page issue</li> <li>Work with both http or https</li> <li>Style improvements</li> <li>Work with both Bootstrap 2 and Bootstrap 3 T3 framework templates</li> </ul><img class="rss-img ja-social-img" src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joomlart/blog/~4/q-IPVa9sqEA" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2016-12-15 17:13:18', 0, '', '2017-07-10 10:18:47', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-07-09 17:18:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"float_fulltext":"","float_intro":"","image_intro":"\\/\\/static.joomlart.com\\/images\\/ja-template\\/ja-builder\\/alpha-release\\/ja-builder-alpha2.jpg","image_intro_alt":"Thanks - JA Joomla Site Builder Alpha 2000+","image_intro_caption":"Thanks - JA Joomla Site Builder Alpha 2000+","image_fulltext":"\\/\\/static.joomlart.com\\/images\\/ja-template\\/ja-builder\\/alpha-release\\/ja-builder-alpha2.jpg","image_fulltext_alt":"Thanks - JA Joomla Site Builder Alpha 2000+","image_fulltext_caption":"Thanks - JA Joomla Site Builder Alpha 2000+"}', '{"targeta":"1","urla":"http:\\/\\/feedproxy.google.com\\/~r\\/joomlart\\/blog\\/~3\\/q-IPVa9sqEA\\/thanks-ja-joomla-site-builder-alpha-2000-downloads-in-2-days-new-version-released-today","