(313, 491, 'New features release : JA K2 filter and search component for Joomla', 'rss-new-features-release-ja-k2-filter-and-search-component-for-joomla', '\n			<p class="intro-text">\n			Hi Guys, Today, JoomlArt team have released new version for JA K2 Filter component - version 1.2.4\n			</p>\n			', '\n			<div class="rss-item content">\n			<p>Hi Guys,</p> <p>Today, JoomlArt team have released new version for JA K2 Filter component - version 1.2.4 with new features, improvements and bug fixes. Here are the details:</p> <ul class="ja-checklist"> <li>New feature: option to make blank page with user\'s defined message before searching</li> <li>New feature: select fields as required fields for searching</li> <li>Improvement: improve search & filter performance</li> <li>Improvement: Update multi ordering for horizontal layout</li> <li>And 2 bug fixes</li> </ul><img class="rss-img ja-social-img" src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joomlart/blog/~4/eRzRbnNBRZA" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2016-10-04 16:49:59', 0, '', '2017-07-10 10:18:47', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-07-09 17:18:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"float_fulltext":"","float_intro":"","image_intro":"\\/\\/static.joomlart.com\\/images\\/blog\\/2016\\/october\\/k2-filter-124\\/k2-filter-release.jpg","image_intro_alt":"New features release : JA K2 filter and search","image_intro_caption":"New features release : JA K2 filter and search","image_fulltext":"\\/\\/static.joomlart.com\\/images\\/blog\\/2016\\/october\\/k2-filter-124\\/k2-filter-release.jpg","image_fulltext_alt":"New features release : JA K2 filter and search","image_fulltext_caption":"New features release : JA K2 filter and search"}', '{"targeta":"1","urla":"http:\\/\\/feedproxy.google.com\\/~r\\/joomlart\\/blog\\/~3\\/eRzRbnNBRZA\\/new-features-release-ja-k2-filter-and-search-component-for-joomla","urlatext":"(Source rss)","targetb":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetc":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":""}', '{}', 1, 0, '', '', 1