(315, 493, 'Introducing the best restaurant Joomla template - JA Restaurant', 'rss-introducing-the-best-restaurant-joomla-template-ja-restaurant', '\n			<p class="intro-text">\n			Welcome our monthly Joomla template - JA Restaurant, a powerful Restaurant Joomla template with\n			</p>\n			', '\n			<div class="rss-item content">\n			<p>Welcome our monthly Joomla template - JA Restaurant, a powerful Restaurant Joomla template with dedicated design and features. It supports 4 menu types, 3 options for Reservation system, useful pre-built pages: Gallery, Offers, About, Happy Hours. The template integrates Open table and Vik Restaurants component.</p><img class="rss-img ja-social-img" src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joomlart/blog/~4/ElqHIQwco8o" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2016-09-20 16:27:44', 0, '', '2017-07-10 10:18:47', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-07-09 17:18:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"float_fulltext":"","float_intro":"","image_intro":"\\/\\/static.joomlart.com\\/images\\/ja-template\\/ja-restaurant\\/review\\/restaurant-joomla-template.jpg","image_intro_alt":"Introducing the best restaurant Joomla template -","image_intro_caption":"Introducing the best restaurant Joomla template -","image_fulltext":"\\/\\/static.joomlart.com\\/images\\/ja-template\\/ja-restaurant\\/review\\/restaurant-joomla-template.jpg","image_fulltext_alt":"Introducing the best restaurant Joomla template -","image_fulltext_caption":"Introducing the best restaurant Joomla template -"}', '{"targeta":"1","urla":"http:\\/\\/feedproxy.google.com\\/~r\\/joomlart\\/blog\\/~3\\/ElqHIQwco8o\\/introducing-the-best-restaurant-joomla-template-ja-restaurant","urlatext":"(Source rss)","targetb":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetc":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":""}', '{}', 1, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{"tags":null}', 0, '*', ''),
(316, 494, 'Updates: JA Promo bar module released with new features and improvement', 'rss-updates-ja-promo-bar-module-released-with-new-features-and-improvement', '\n			<p class="intro-text">\n			Hi Guys, Today, JoomlArt team have just released new version for JA Promo Bar module - version 1.0.4\n			</p>\n			', '\n			<div class="rss-item content">\n			<p>Hi Guys,</p> <p>Today, JoomlArt team have just released new version for JA Promo Bar module - version 1.0.4 with new features and improvements. The free Joomla extension serves to display a promotion bar on the top position of your site which can includes a message, cool countdown timer, link or button, image or color background, inline image/icon, can be sticky and integrate Google URL Builder. It is responsive.</p><img class="rss-img ja-social-img" src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joomlart/blog/~4/0RNtRPKvRog" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>\n			</div>', 1, 14, '2016-09-05 17:36:48', 0, '', '2017-07-10 10:18:47', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-07-09 17:18:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"float_fulltext":"","float_intro":"","image_intro":"\\/\\/static.joomlart.com\\/images\\/blog\\/2016\\/august\\/JA-Promo-bar-release.jpg","image_intro_alt":"Updates: JA Promo bar module released with new","image_intro_caption":"Updates: JA Promo bar module released with new","image_fulltext":"\\/\\/static.joomlart.com\\/images\\/blog\\/2016\\/august\\/JA-Promo-bar-release.jpg","image_fulltext_alt":"Updates: JA Promo bar module released with new","image_fulltext_caption":"Updates: JA Promo bar module released with new"}', '{"targeta":"1","urla":"http:\\/\\/feedproxy.google.com\\/~r\\/joomlart\\/blog\\/~3\\/0RNtRPKvRog\\/updates-ja-promo-bar-module-released-with-new-features-and-improvement","urlatext":"(Source rss)","targetb":"","urlb":null,"urlbtext":"","targetc":"","urlc":null,"urlctext":""}', '{}', 1, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{"tags":null}', 0, '*', ''),
