(798, 305, 1, '', '2017-07-10 10:08:09', 42, 3004, 'a9034f53435be9a9aae959f1c1f165cf0bba29d3', '{"id":305,"asset_id":483,"title":"Advanced Joomla Filter extension released - JA Megafilter","alias":"rss-advanced-joomla-filter-extension-released-ja-megafilter","introtext":"\\n\\t\\t\\t<p class=\\"intro-text\\">\\n\\t\\t\\tDid you know, our JA BrickStore template featuring VirtueMart has a new cool filter extension?\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t","fulltext":"\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"rss-item content\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p>Did you know, our JA BrickStore template featuring VirtueMart has a new cool filter extension? Incase, you missed it, you can view it live on <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/ja-brickstore.demo.joomlart.com\\/index.php\\/en\\/ja-megafilter\\" title=\\"JA Megafilter for virtuemart\\" target=\\"_blank\\">demo<\\/a>. We received lots of requests to include support for more popular extensions for the MegaFilter and today we are releasing JA MegaFilter with native support for JoomShopping, E-Shop, K2 component, HikaShop and Virtuemart. JA MegaFilter is a Joomla search and filter extension to build search and filter pages for popular Joomla extensions. The Joomla filter extension includes base field filters like title, tags, category, price, manufacturer, brand etc and custom field filter like color or size. For k2 it also supports the author and category fields apart from tags.<\\/p> <p>Megafilter with virtuemart plugin is available for free to club members and can be downloaded from JA BrickStore template download section. Rest of the plugins are released under extension club and can also be purchased as single extension. As always our Developer members gets complimentary free access. <\\/p><img class=\\"rss-img ja-social-img\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/feeds.feedburner.com\\/~r\\/joomlart\\/blog\\/~4\\/DM9nJLRKy8k\\" height=\\"1\\" width=\\"1\\" alt=\\"\\"\\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>","state":1,"catid":"14","created":"2016-12-28 15:54:53","created_by":0,"created_by_alias":"","mod